        "timestamp": "2020-08-03 12:57:46.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nUpdated docker file, to include openJDK 11.0.8 image, instead of openjdk 11.0.6.\nWe have seen some memory leaks in our environments (DFC survives +/- 2 hours, then restarts with outOfMemory exceptions). We noticed openJDK 11.0.7 comes with some fixes on this, as well as a number of TLS handling fixes. Let`s try to update to openJDK 11.0.8 and see, if issues persist.\n\n(We haven`t see this behavior on prior version of openJDK in the past for DFC)",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
